welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Fife, a charming city known for its rich history, beautiful nature, and friendly locals. We invite you to explore our vibrant community and create unforgettable memories during your stay. Enjoy your time in Fife!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at McChord AFB Airport serves both civilian and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at McChord AFB Airport is exclusively for military personnel and their families.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Industrial Airport houses all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Industrial Airport handles all freight and cargo shipments.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves as the primary hub for all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport primarily serves Alaska Airlines and its partners.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves as the hub for international flights and some domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport serves as the primary hub for all commercial flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Renton Airport caters to private and smaller aircrafts.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, free of charge.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all commercial flights at Boeing Field/King County International Airport.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal primarily serves general aviation and cargo flights at Boeing Field/King County International Airport.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bremerton Airport is a small, single-story building with a few amenities for passengers.

terminals.name: Private Hangar
terminals.description: The private hangar at Bremerton Airport is used for private aircraft storage and maintenance.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, but may have limited speed and connectivity.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the terminal building.
